textBeforeTable: Exos round semi-flush ceiling mount features a glass shade with metal accents and bottom glass diffuser. Glass available in Opal, Stone, and Pearl. Finish available in Mahogany, Bronze, Dark Smoke, Burnished Steel, Black, or Natural Iron. One 100 watt 120 volt A19 lamp medium base incandescent lamp not included. 8.55 inches high x 6 inch diameter. UL listed for damp location.
